body:
So I just had a game where I was legitimately curious as to why this Trist was building rageblade first up with no on hit effects. My question was legit &quot;Why&#039;re you building that if you have no on-hit effects?&quot; The response I got was &quot;stfu&quot; and &quot;stay bronze %%%&quot;, I digress. I further stated to this player that Trist doesn&#039;t really have a natural synergy with the item other than her AP scalings now. 

Anyways , irrc Tris has no innate on hit abilities to make use of the sated rageblade, and the cost/cost efficiency at 0 stacks seems to delay her spikes even possibly costing the game. The only way I can see it being useful on her is with BotrK/Wits End/Nashors tooth and a full on hit build which I assume would be suboptimal? 

Do people find that players don&#039;t want to take this feedback/advice on? {{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
